---
// Wrapper typographique pour le corps d'article.
// Site en thème clair → `prose` par défaut (texte sombre sur fond clair), accents orange sur les liens.
// Les body/listes gardent les gris lisibles du plugin typography ; on n'override que titres, strong, liens, code, blockquote.
---
<div
  class="prose prose-lg max-w-none
    prose-headings:text-foreground prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-headings:scroll-mt-24
    prose-h2:mt-14 prose-h2:text-2xl md:prose-h2:text-3xl
    prose-h3:mt-10 prose-h3:text-xl md:prose-h3:text-2xl
    prose-strong:text-foreground
    prose-a:text-primary prose-a:font-semibold prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline
    prose-blockquote:border-l-primary prose-blockquote:bg-primary/5 prose-blockquote:rounded-r-lg prose-blockquote:py-1 prose-blockquote:not-italic
    prose-code:text-foreground prose-code:bg-muted prose-code:rounded prose-code:px-1.5 prose-code:py-0.5 prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none
    prose-table:text-sm prose-th:text-foreground
    prose-img:rounded-xl prose-img:border prose-img:border-border"
>
  <slot />
</div>
